00:45:56.000 --> 00:45:56.880
Tibetan butter tea

00:45:56.880 --> 00:45:58.810
ay isang tradisyonal na inuming Tibetan

00:45:59.030 --> 00:46:01.190
nagmula sa Qinghai-Tibet Plateau ng Tsina

00:46:01.190 --> 00:46:02.920
na may kasaysayang mahigit isang libong taon.

00:46:02.920 --> 00:46:04.230
